works.description:
This image is of our Agile Design /  
Development Model.  We created the image as an original document, it is  
part of our sales and marketing materials.  I have been watching a steady 

decline in traffic to our site based on the dilution of our Google Images 

SEO on this image.  In fact our image no longer returns in the result and 

our traffic has taken a complete nose-dive as a result.  One or more of
the  
infringing parties may have reported us to get our image removed.  This is
 
highly unfortunate, but we wish to have our ranking restored as they are  

dealt with appropriately.
